-26T23:35:01Z — OK\n   514→- **Log**: iteration-018.log\n   515→\n   516→## Iteration 19 — Bankrun test suite completeness check\n   517→\n   518→**Item**: Phase E, item 1 — Bankrun test suite for lord program (≥15 tests)\n   519→\n   520→**What was done**:\n   521→- Audited existing 30 lordofrngs bankrun tests against spec requirements\n   522→- Identified 3 missing edge case tests and added them:\n   523→  1. `join_round` — \"rejects join when phase is Locked\" (replaced empty placeholder with real test: creates Locked round via start_spin, verifies 3rd player rejected with InvalidPhase)\n   524→  2. `buy_more_entries` — \"rejects buy_more_entries when phase is Locked\" (new test: creates Locked round, verifies buy_more_entries rejected with InvalidPhase)\n   525→  3. `claim_payout` — \"rejects double-claim (round PDA closed after first claim)\" (new test: claims once, verifies second claim fails because PDA no longer exists)\n   526→- Note: profile CPI test listed in spec requirements cannot be tested because lordofrngs claim_payout does not have platform CPI wired (was deferred in iteration 7; game_type discriminator was added to platform in iteration 10 but CPI call not added to lordofrngs claim_payout). The claim_payout instruction already has correct fee + payout logic tested.\n   527→\n   528→**Final test count**: 38 lordofrngs tests (well above ≥15 target), covering all 8 instructions:\n   529→- initialize_config: 1 test\n   530→- create_round: 5 tests (happy path, multiple entries, round counter, invalid tier, zero entries)\n   531→- join_round: 6 tests (happy/countdown trigger, 3rd player, multiple entries, duplicate, max 20, wrong phase)\n   532→- buy_more_entries: 5 tests (happy, active phase, not in round, zero entries, wrong phase)\n   533→- start_spin: 4 tests (happy, idempotent, too early, wrong phase)\n   534→- claim_payout: 8 tests (creator wins, player2 wins, multiple entries, PDA closed, unfulfilled VRF, wrong winner, wrong phase, double-claim)\n   535→- timeout_refund: 5 tests (happy, proportional, VRF fulfilled reject, too early, wrong phase)\n   536→- force_close: 4 tests (waiting round, active round, non-admin, locked round)\n   537→\n   538→**Verification**: All tests pass separately:\n   539→- lordofrngs: 38 tests passing\n   540→- coinflip: 26 tests passing (no regressions)\n   541→- platform: 5 tests passing (no regressions)\n   542→\n   543→**Status**: Done\n   544→\n   545→## Iteration 19 — 2026-02-26T23:40:14Z — OK\n   546→- **Log**: iteration-019.log\n   547→\n   548→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"099dd0b0-a222-4d0c-a064-f7a4d8b48847","uuid":"20bc30b8-1859-4d6f-93e1-3f51010be5f1","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/101-lord-of-the-rngs/history.md","content":"# Implementation History — 101-lord-of-the-rngs\n\nIteration log for the autonomous spec loop. Each entry records what was\nattempted and whether it succeeded. The agent reads this file at the start\nof every iteration to understand prior context.\n\n---\n\n## Iteration 1 — Scaffold lordofrngs program\n\n**Item**: Phase A, item 1 — Scaffold `solana/programs/lordofrngs/`\n\n**What was done**:\n- Created `programs/lordofrngs/` directory with full structure:\n  - `Cargo.toml` — mirrors coinflip dependencies (anchor-lang, rng-shared, platform CPI, orao-solana-vrf), same feature flags including mock-vrf default\n  - `Xargo.toml` — standard BPF target config\n  - `src/lib.rs` — `declare_id!(\"B9Lufh9GvuucDxDRZBr3qPNe4cJaS5MQBQKZxgUT5qYa\")`, program module with `initialize_config` instruction stub\n  - `src/state.rs` — `LordConfig` (PDA `[b\"lord_config\"]`, authority/treasury/paused/round_counters/bump), `PlayerEntry` (player pubkey + u32 entries), `JackpotRound` (PDA `[b\"jackpot_round\", tier, round_number]`, full round state with Vec<PlayerEntry> max 20), `RoundSettled` event\n  - `src/error.rs` — `LordError` enum with 13 error codes (6100–6112)\n  - `src/instructions/mod.rs` + 