{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01PjYakwH8CSLk839qjDuUMR","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I now have comprehensive information. Let me compile the findings.\n\n---\n\n## Visual Testing Setup - Comprehensive Analysis\n\n### 1. Visual Test Framework & Location\n\n**Framework**: **Playwright** (`@playwright/test` v1.58.2)\n\n**Visual test files location**:\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/visual/`\n- Two test suites:\n  - `routes.spec.ts` - Route/page baseline snapshots\n  - `states.spec.ts` - State variant snapshots (wallet connected/disconnected, error states)\n\n### 2. Script Commands\n\nFrom `apps/platform/package.json`:\n\n```bash\npnpm test:visual            # Run visual regression tests (default config)\npnpm test:visual:update     # Update snapshot baselines with --update-snapshots flag\n```\n\nThese map to:\n- `\"test:visual\": \"playwright test\"` (uses `playwright.config.ts`)\n- `\"test:visual:update\": \"playwright test --update-snapshots\"`\n\n### 3. Playwright Configurations\n\nFour separate configs exist for different testing contexts:\n\n| Config File | Purpose | Port | Web Server | Test Match |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| `playwright.config.ts` | **Visual regression tests** (default) | 3000 | `pnpm dev` with `VITE_MOCK_MODE=true` | `visual/**/*.spec.ts` |\n| `playwright.local.config.ts` | Local E2E integration tests | 3002 | Vite dev server | `local/**/*.spec.ts` |\n| `playwright.devnet.config.ts` | Devnet E2E tests | 3003 | Vite dev server | `devnet/**/*.spec.ts` |\n| `playwright.real.config.ts` | Real wallet mode tests | 3001 | Vite dev server | `real/**/*.spec.ts` |\n\n**Key visual regression config settings** (`playwright.config.ts`):\n- **Test directory**: `./e2e`\n- **Project filter**: `visual/**/*.spec.ts` only\n- **Browser**: Desktop Chrome (1280×1080 viewport)\n- **Snapshot path template**: `{testDir}/__snapshots__/{testFilePath}/{arg}{ext}`\n- **Max diff pixel ratio**: 0.015 (1.5% allowed difference)\n- **Workers**: 1 (serial execution)\n- **Web server**: Starts with `VITE_MOCK_MODE=true` for mock wallet/RNG\n- **Snapshot update**: Uses `--update-snapshots` flag\n\n### 4. Baseline Images Storage\n\n**Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/__snapshots__/visual/`\n\n**Structure**:\n```\ne2e/__snapshots__/visual/\n├── routes.spec.ts/          (12 route baselines)\n│   ├── 404.png\n│   ├── close-call.png\n│   ├── coinflip.png\n│   ├── crash.png\n│   ├── fairness.png\n│   ├── game-of-trades.png\n│   ├── home.png\n│   ├── leaderboard.png\n│   ├── loot.png\n│   ├── lord-of-rngs.png\n│   ├── profile.png\n│   └── quests.png\n└── states.spec.ts/          (6 state/variant baselines)\n    ├── home-connected.png\n    ├── home-disconnected.png\n    ├── coinflip-connected.png\n    ├── coinflip-disconnected.png\n    ├── coinflip-error-toast-position.png\n    └── profile-connected.png\n```\n\n**Total**: 18 baseline PNG files (~1.1-1.3 MB each, ~21 MB total)\n\n### 5. Test File Details\n\n#### `routes.spec.ts` (Route baselines)\n- **Purpose**: Verify visual baseline for each major route\n- **Tests** (12 total):\n  - home page\n  - coinflip page\n  - **lord of rngs page** ✓ (includes Lord of the RNGs)\n  - close call page\n  - crash page\n  - game of trades page\n  - profile page\n  - quests page\n  - loot page\n  - fairness page\n  - leaderboard page\n  - 404 page\n- **Screenshot approach**: Full page, uses `stablePage` fixture\n\n```typescript\ntest(\"lord of rngs page\", async ({ stablePage }) => {\n  await stablePage.goto(\"/lord-of-rngs\");\n  await expect(stablePage).toHaveScreenshot(\"lord-of-rngs.png\", { fullPage: true });\n});\n```\n\n#### `states.spec.ts` (State variants)\n- **Purpose**: Test UI states (wallet connected/disconnected, error conditions)\n- **Test groups** (6 total baselines):\n  1. **Home page** - disconnected state\n  2. **Home page** - connected state (with wallet interaction)\n  3. **Coinflip page** - disconnected state\n  4. **Coinflip page** - connected state (includes error toast positioning test)\n  5. **Coinflip page** - error toast below middle container\n  6. **Profile page** - connected state\n- **Fixture interaction patterns**:\n  - Clears localStorage: `localStorage.removeItem(\"rng-utopia-mock-wallet\")`\n  - Clicks wallet icon: `.rpg-wallet-icon`\n  - Waits for connection: `.rpg-wallet-icon--connected`\n  - Pauses animations before snapshot\n  - Waits 300ms for UI stabilization\n\n### 6. Visual Regression Setup (`stablePage` Fixture)\n\n**Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/fixtures.ts`\n\n**Fixture features** (all executed for determinism):\n\n1. **Deterministic PRNG**: Mulberry32 seeded PRNG (seed=42) overrides `Math.random()` and `crypto.getRandomValues()`\n2. **Frozen time**: `Date.now()` frozen to 2026-01-01T00:00:00Z (1767225600000)\n3. **Animation freezing**: Injects CSS to disable all CSS transitions/animations/transitions (duration 0s)\n4. **SVG pause**: Pauses SVG SMIL animations via `svg.pauseAnimations()`\n5. **Font loading**: Waits for `document.fonts.ready`\n6. **Network idle**: `waitUntil: \"networkidle\"` on navigation\n7. **Settle time**: 300ms additional wait for paint stabilization\n8. **Error detection**: Collects console errors and fails test if any occur\n\n**Fixture CSS injection**:\n```css\n*, *::before, *::after {\n  animation-duration: 0s !important;\n  animation-delay: 0s !important;\n  transition-duration: 0s !important;\n  transition-delay: 0s !important;\n  scroll-behavior: auto !important;\n}\nsvg { animation-play-state: paused !important; }\n```\n\n### 7. Visual Test Files for Lord of the RNGs & Coinflip\n\n**Existing Lord of the RNGs coverage**:\n- Route baseline: `/e2e/__snapshots__/visual/routes.spec.ts/lord-of-rngs.png`\n- Test: `routes.spec.ts` lines 14-17\n\n**Existing Coinflip coverage**:\n- Route baseline: `/e2e/__snapshots__/visual/routes.spec.ts/coinflip.png`\n- State variants:\n  - `/e2e/__snapshots__/visual/states.spec.ts/coinflip-connected.png`\n  - `/e2e/__snapshots__/visual/states.spec.ts/coinflip-disconnected.png`\n  - `/e2e/__snapshots__/visual/states.spec.ts/coinflip-error-toast-position.png`\n- Tests: `states.spec.ts` lines 87-167\n\n### 8. Key Architecture Insights\n\n**Test environment isolation**:\n- **Visual tests** run against **mock mode** (`VITE_MOCK_MODE=true`) for reproducibility\n- **E2E tests** (local/devnet) run against **real programs** with test wallets\n- **Real mode tests** run against Devnet or live wallets\n\n**Turbo config** (turbo.json):\n- `test:visual` task has `\"cache\": false` (never cached, always runs fresh)\n\n**Framework dependencies**:\n- `@playwright/test@^1.58.2` (dev dependency)\n- Uses Playwright's built-in `toHaveScreenshot()` matcher\n- No additional snapshot library (jest-image-snapshot, etc.) needed\n\n### 9. Development Workflow\n\n**Running visual tests**:\n```bash\ncd /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia\npnpm test:visual              # Runs visual regression tests against baselines\npnpm test:visual:update       # Updates baselines after intentional UI changes\n```\n\n**Alternatively via root**:\n```bash\ncd /workspaces/rng-utopia\npnpm test:visual              # Turbo delegates to apps/platform\npnpm test:visual:update       # (update command not exposed at root level)\n```\n\n---\n\n## Summary Table\n\n| Question | Answer |\n|----------|--------|\n| **Where are visual tests defined?** | `/apps/platform/e2e/visual/` (2 test files: `routes.spec.ts`, `states.spec.ts`) |\n| **Test framework?** | Playwright (`@playwright/test` v1.58.2) with snapshot matching |\n| **Baseline images location?** | `/apps/platform/e2e/__snapshots__/visual/` (18 PNG files, ~21 MB total) |\n| **Update command?** | `pnpm test:visual:update` (flag: `--update-snapshots`) |\n| **Run command?** | `pnpm test:visual` (default Playwright config) |\n| **Lord of the RNGs c